Package cs113.calendar.util

Exception Summary
CommandFormatException Thrown when a user-entered command does not conform to the expected format.
DateFormatException An incorrectly formatted string date.
DuplicateUserIdException User ID is the same as one that already exists.
IdenticalAppointmentException Thrown when an appointment cannot be added because it is the same as an existing one.
InvalidDateException A date that was not meaninful.
ModelMismatchException Thrown if the incorrect concrete model type is passed to a model backend.
NoSuchAppointmentException The appointment you are looking for does not exist.
NoSuchCommandException Thrown when CommandLineEngine can't find the command we asked for.
NoSuchUserException The user ID you requested does not exist.
StorageException Something went wrong in the backend.
